<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:07:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登支持以色列的说法，称加沙医院爆炸是“其他团队”造成的</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/biden-backs-israels-claim-says-gaza-hospital-blast-done-by-other-team/articleshow/104523037.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104523037.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统拜登表示，造成一百多人死亡的加沙医院爆炸是对方造成的，这与以色列政府关于哈马斯火箭弹失火的说法一致。拜登访问特拉维夫声援以色列，他也对爆炸事件表示悲伤和愤怒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 09:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/biden-backs-israels-claim-says-gaza-hospital-blast-done-by-other-team/articleshow/104523037.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞西表示，埃及拒绝让巴勒斯坦人流离失所到西奈半岛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-rejects-any-displacement-of-palestinians-into-sinai-says-sisi/articleshow/104523560.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104523560.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西周三表示，埃及人将拒绝强迫数百万巴勒斯坦人流离失所到西奈半岛，并补充说任何此类举动都将把该半岛变成针对以色列的袭击基地。塞西在开罗与德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨举行的联合新闻发布会上表示，加沙地带实际上处于以色列控制之下，巴勒斯坦人可能会被转移到以色列的内盖夫沙漠，“直到武装分子得到解决”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 09:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-rejects-any-displacement-of-palestinians-into-sinai-says-sisi/articleshow/104523560.cms</guid></item><item><title>大英博物馆在盗窃事件发生后将其全部藏品数字化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/british-museum-to-digitise-its-entire-collection-after-theft-incident/articleshow/104523365.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104523365.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;大英博物馆周三表示，在八月份报道了一起导致数百件文物失踪的盗窃事件后，计划将其全部藏品数字化。大英博物馆临时馆长马克·琼斯在一份声明中表示：“我们已采取措施加强安全，现在相信此类盗窃行为不会再发生。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 09:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/british-museum-to-digitise-its-entire-collection-after-theft-incident/articleshow/104523365.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击后，立法者敦促白宫打击哈马斯使用加密货币</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lawmakers-urge-white-house-to-crackdown-on-hamas-use-of-crypto-after-israel-attack/articleshow/104522900.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104522900.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一个由两党议员组成的小组敦促拜登政府对哈马斯及其附属机构使用加密货币采取行动。立法者对数字资产被用来资助运营和逃避美国制裁表示担忧。以色列当局已经从与哈马斯相关的地址中扣押了数百万美元的加密货币。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 09:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lawmakers-urge-white-house-to-crackdown-on-hamas-use-of-crypto-after-israel-attack/articleshow/104522900.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国反犹太主义事件增多，柏林犹太教堂遭到燃烧弹袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-berlin-synagogue-is-attacked-with-firebombs-while-antisemitic-incidents-rise-in-germany/articleshow/104522338.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104522338.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中东暴力事件后，柏林的一座犹太教堂遭到燃烧瓶袭击，反犹太主义事件不断增加。 Kahal Adass Jisroel 社区证实了这起袭击事件，警方正在调查该事件。德国主要犹太组织表示，有两人参与了此次袭击。犹太人中央委员会对此表示震惊，并表示哈马斯的意识形态正在德国产生影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 08:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-berlin-synagogue-is-attacked-with-firebombs-while-antisemitic-incidents-rise-in-germany/articleshow/104522338.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争：英国间谍局长警告中东冲突造成恐怖威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/israel-hamas-war-uk-spy-chief-warns-of-terror-threat-from-middle-east-conflict/articleshow/104522027.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104522027.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国国内军情五处情报机构负责人警告说，当前以色列和巴勒斯坦领土上的冲突增加了英国的恐怖风险，并特别指出伊朗是一个令人担忧的问题。在专门针对伊朗的讲话中，他指出伦敦“长期以来”一直“担心”伊朗在英国境内的行为，而当前的中东局势加剧了这些担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 08:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/israel-hamas-war-uk-spy-chief-warns-of-terror-threat-from-middle-east-conflict/articleshow/104522027.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京访华期间俄罗斯核案件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-filmed-in-china-accompanied-by-officers-with-russian-nuclear-briefcase/articleshow/104521684.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104521684.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三罕见的镜头显示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在北京陪同官员携带所谓的核公文包，该公文包可用于下令进行核打击。普京在北京与中国国家主席习近平会面后，被拍到步行到另一次会议由保安包围，后面跟着两名身穿制服的俄罗斯海军军官，每人都提着公文包。镜头拉近其中一个公文包。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 08:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-filmed-in-china-accompanied-by-officers-with-russian-nuclear-briefcase/articleshow/104521684.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着巴贝特风暴逼近，英国各地预计将迎来“一个月的降雨”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/as-storm-babet-approaches-months-worth-rain-expected-across-uk/articleshow/104506762.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104506762.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国气象局已发布风暴巴贝特恶劣天气警报，预计将为英国带来大雨。预计风暴将于周三登陆，从英格兰东南部到苏格兰的地区预计将受到影响。英国气象局警告称，存在洪水风险，特别是在苏格兰东部、北爱尔兰和英格兰北部。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/as-storm-babet-approaches-months-worth-rain-expected-across-uk/articleshow/104506762.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争：新加坡以安全为由禁止与以色列-哈马斯冲突有关的公共集会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/israel-hamas-war-singapore-bars-public-assemblies-related-to-israel-hamas-conflict-cites-security-concerns/articleshow/104520624.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104520624.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新加坡当局宣布，出于对公共安全的担忧，将不允许举行与以色列-哈马斯冲突有关的活动和公众集会。警方和国家公园管理局表示，组织此类活动的申请将被拒绝。警方还警告不要对种族或宗教发表麻木不仁或冒犯性的言论，因为这可能会危及新加坡的种族和宗教和谐。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 07:54:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/israel-hamas-war-singapore-bars-public-assemblies-related-to-israel-hamas-conflict-cites-security-concerns/articleshow/104520624.cms</guid></item><item><title>柬埔寨反对派人物Thach Setha被判入狱三年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cambodian-opposition-figure-thach-setha-jailed-for-three-years/articleshow/104519088.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104519088.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三，柬埔寨一家法院判处一名高级反对派人物三年监禁，原因是他在社交媒体上发帖讨论种族灭绝的红色高棉政权垮台的争议历史。反对党烛光党副主席 Thach Setha 一月份在 Facebook 上发布了一段视频，讨论 1 月 7 日的政治敏感历史，但他的批评言论引起了当局的愤怒，指控他在 7 月选举前煽动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 07:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cambodian-opposition-figure-thach-setha-jailed-for-three-years/articleshow/104519088.cms</guid></item><item><title>杀害法国教师的嫌疑人已接受正式调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/suspect-in-killing-of-french-teacher-put-under-formal-investigation/articleshow/104517907.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104517907.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:25:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/suspect-in-killing-of-french-teacher-put-under-formal-investigation/articleshow/104517907.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙医院爆炸后，约旦取消美国总统拜登与阿拉伯领导人的峰会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jordan-cancels-us-president-biden-summit-with-arab-leaders-after-gaza-hospital-blast/articleshow/104515380.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104515380.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;约旦取消了与美国总统乔·拜登以及埃及和巴勒斯坦领导人讨论加沙局势的峰会。约旦外交部长艾曼·萨法迪表示，只有在达成结束针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力的协议后才会举行会议。峰会的取消反映出拜登访问以色列期间该地区局势动荡。白宫表示，由于加沙医院发生爆炸，拜登推迟了对约旦的访问。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:03:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jordan-cancels-us-president-biden-summit-with-arab-leaders-after-gaza-hospital-blast/articleshow/104515380.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平在与普京的会谈中赞扬中俄之间的“加深”信任</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/xi-hails-deepening-trust-between-china-russia-in-talks-with-putin/articleshow/104516122.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104516122.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平在同俄罗斯总统普京会谈时强调，中俄政治互信不断深化。习近平呼吁共同维护国际公平正义，强调两国密切战略协作。双边贸易额创历史新高，向双方确定的2000亿美元目标迈进。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:33:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/xi-hails-deepening-trust-between-china-russia-in-talks-with-putin/articleshow/104516122.cms</guid></item><item><title>弗拉基米尔·普京：在困难的世界中与中国的密切协调至关重要</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/close-coordination-with-china-crucial-in-a-difficult-world-vladimir-putin/articleshow/104514221.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104514221.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/close-coordination-with-china-crucial-in-a-difficult-world-vladimir-putin/articleshow/104514221.cms</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼公布了中国飞机数百次“高度关注”飞机拦截的镜头</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pentagon-releases-footage-of-hundreds-of-highly-concerning-aircraft-intercepts-by-chinese-planes/articleshow/104513959.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104513959.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五角大楼公布的视频显示，过去两年中国飞机拦截美国战机的次数超过 180 次，比过去十年的总和还多。美国军方官员对这一趋势感到担忧，并认为这是中国更大的地区恐吓模式的一部分。尽管中国的航班被认为具有风险和攻击性，但它们并未被归类为不安全。然而，官员们认为这种行为可能会导致事故或冲突。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pentagon-releases-footage-of-hundreds-of-highly-concerning-aircraft-intercepts-by-chinese-planes/articleshow/104513959.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主席习近平与俄罗斯总统普京在北京举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-russias-putin-hold-talks-in-beijing/articleshow/104513821.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104513821.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-russias-putin-hold-talks-in-beijing/articleshow/104513821.cms</guid></item><item><title>被以色列指责为加沙医院爆炸事件的伊斯兰圣战组织是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-islamic-jihad-the-group-being-blamed-by-israel-for-bombing-at-gaza-hospital/articleshow/104513381.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104513381.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙一家医院的爆炸引发了愤怒和抗议，以色列和巴勒斯坦人相互指责。 1981年成立的巴勒斯坦激进组织伊斯兰圣战组织与该事件有牵连。伊斯兰圣战组织反对与以色列的和平进程，并寻求在巴勒斯坦建立一个伊斯兰国家。该组织主要在加沙活动，并对以色列目标进行了袭击。它与哈马斯结盟，并得到伊朗和叙利亚的支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:46:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-islamic-jihad-the-group-being-blamed-by-israel-for-bombing-at-gaza-hospital/articleshow/104513381.cms</guid></item><item><title>谁应对加沙致命爆炸负责：伊斯兰圣战组织还是以色列？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-what-we-know-about-the-deadly-blast-at-a-gaza-city-hospital/articleshow/104512787.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104512787.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据哈马斯管理的卫生部称，加沙城的阿赫利医院周二发生巨大爆炸，造成数百名受伤或在那里寻求庇护的巴勒斯坦人死亡。该部表示，至少 500 人在阿赫利医院爆炸中死亡。以色列国防部表示，爆炸是由以色列空袭造成的，但以色列军方表示，这是伊斯兰圣战组织发射的火箭，这是一个与哈马斯结盟的规模较小、更为极端的巴勒斯坦激进派别。该部表示，至少 500 人在阿赫利医院爆炸中死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-what-we-know-about-the-deadly-blast-at-a-gaza-city-hospital/articleshow/104512787.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争：国际法如何适用于战争以及为什么哈马斯和以色列都被指控违反了国际法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-how-international-law-applies-to-war-and-why-hamas-and-israel-are-both-alleged-to-have-broken-it/articleshow/104512820.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104512820.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国正在收集哈马斯-以色列冲突各方所犯战争罪的证据。武装冲突规则受国际公认的法律和决议管辖，包括《联合国宪章》和《日内瓦公约》。国际刑事法院有权起诉战争罪，但一些国家不承认其管辖权。其他国际和国内法院也可以审理与涉嫌违法行为有关的案件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:21:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-how-international-law-applies-to-war-and-why-hamas-and-israel-are-both-alleged-to-have-broken-it/articleshow/104512820.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯冲突：联合国秘书长古特雷斯呼吁“立即人道主义停火”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-conflict-united-nations-antonio-guterres-calls-for-immediate-humanitarian-ceasefire/articleshow/104513457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104513457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯周三呼吁以色列和巴勒斯坦武装分子在加沙的冲突“立即实现人道主义停火”。古特雷斯说：“我呼吁立即实行人道主义停火……”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-conflict-united-nations-antonio-guterres-calls-for-immediate-humanitarian-ceasefire/articleshow/104513457.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>